<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - ABC Retailers</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f7f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #3498db;
            margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ul, ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .intro {
            background-color: #f1f8ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .contact {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .date {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <div class="intro">
            <p>ABC Retailers is committed to protecting the privacy of our customers. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you shop on our website.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and shipping address when you create an account or make a purchase.</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit card numbers when you make a purchase.</li>
            <li><strong>Browsing Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, and device type when you visit our website.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Order Fulfillment:</strong> Process and fulfill your orders.</li>
            <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Contact you about orders, promotions, and updates.</li>
            <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> Send marketing emails and promotions (you can opt-out anytime).</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Analyze website traffic and improve our services.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Payment processors and shipping companies to fulfill orders.</li>
            <li><strong>Partners:</strong> Affiliates to offer relevant promotions.</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> If required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Security Measures</h2>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> Protect payment information.</li>
            <li><strong>Secure Servers:</strong> Store personal information on protected servers.</li>
            <li><strong>Access Control:</strong> Limit access to authorized personnel only.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> View and update your information by logging into your account.</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing emails.</li>
            <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Request account deletion by contacting us.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Changes to this Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy and will notify you by posting the updated version on our website.</p>

        <div class="contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at support@abcretailers.com.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="date">Effective as of September 1, 2025</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>